" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"text-anchor: middle; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><tspan dy=\"0\" alignment-baseline=\"mathematical\">God node. Owns cycle timer, status display, system tray icon. Orchestrates all services.</tspan></text></g><g class=\"person-man\"><rect x=\"200\" y=\"1052\" fill=\"#85BBF0\" stroke=\"#78A8D8\" width=\"430\" height=\"105\" rx=\"2.5\" ry=\"2.5\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"></rect><text fill=\"#FFFFFF\" font-family=\"&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-style=\"italic\" lengthAdjust=\"spacing\" textLength=\"73\" x=\"378.5\" y=\"1072\">&lt;&lt;component&gt;&gt;</text><text x=\"415\" y=\"1090\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"text-anchor: middle; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><tspan dy=\"0\" alignment-baseline=\"mathematical\">SettingsForm</tspan></text><text x=\"415\" y=\"1112\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" font-style=\"italic\" style=\"text-anchor: middle; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><tspan dy=\"0\" alignment-baseline=\"mathematical\">[WinForms Form]</tspan></text><text x=\"415\" y=\"1146\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"text-anchor: middle; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><tspan dy=\"0\" alignment-baseline=\"mathematical\">UI for VPN type, cycle duration, MEGAsync path, theme selection.</tspan></text></g><g class=\"person-man\"><rect x=\"200\" y=\"1257\" fill=\"#85BBF0\" stroke=\"#78A8D8\" width=\"328\" height=\"105\" rx=\"2.5\" ry=\"2.5\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"></rect><text fill=\"#FFFFFF\" font-family=\"&quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif\" font-size=\"12\" font-style=\"italic\" lengthAdjust=\"spacing\" textLength=\"73\" x=\"327.5\" y=\"1277\">&lt;&lt;component&gt;&gt;</text><text x=\"364\" y=\"1295\" dominant-ba